Human Language: english
>Description:
After submitting a bug-report, the keyboard focus is left in some hidden
place, but whatever that place is, hitting space again re-submits the bug
(as nicely demonstrated by my last triple-submission).

It looks like what happens is that the "Submit" button is hidden and "Abort"
is shown instead, but the "Submit" still has the keyboard focus.  If this is
correct then one thing is for the bug dialog to switch the focus to the close
button, but also on the MrEd level, I don't think that it's healthy to leave
the keyboard focus on hidden things.
